    "text": "Seniors in the Workforce Tax Relief Act\n\nThis bill allows an above-the-line tax deduction through 2028 for individual taxpayers who have attained age 65 at the end of the taxable year. The deduction is equal to $25,000 reduced by a percentage of the taxpayer's adjusted gross income.\u00a0"
